WeatherVibe.Profile.Badlands.Autumn.3=5,3,20,40
WeatherVibe.Profile.Badlands.Autumn.4=25,22,30,60
WeatherVibe.Profile.Badlands.Autumn.5=15,41,30,60

# Winter: cooler but still dry, occasional fog in valleys, dust calmer
