# Duskwood  -  Cursed, perpetually dark forest
# Theme: Eternal twilight, thick fog, haunted atmosphere.
# Fog is THE dominant weather. Light rain drips through canopy.
# Never truly "fine"  -  even clear moments feel dark.
# No snow, no thunderstorms  -  just quiet, creeping dread.
#======================================================================

